      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;sect1&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;_erp_design&#34;&gt;ERP Design&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sectionbody&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sect2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;_context&#34;&gt;Context&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;imageblock kroki&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://kroki.io/plantuml/svg/eNqNVMtu2zAQvOsrWJ1kILEaoKeeYitu0CB2Dbvx1VhTG4koRQokhVQt-u9dSrIerhH05KV3ZvYxC91bB8ZVhQw-CMVllWJlJMudK-3nODbwNs-Ey6tTZdFwrRwqN-e6iHeCg0n1RmCJMk4-3W4lKPeyfo4NSgSL8d3tR_r_mBAJhEIzL32VYIvGahVZkGjLJr5h4d6_2EplBEQTzs4o4FxXxFeOQIv-MQAKUJChoey6jSgV7GvrsDguCZ2CqSN-R3niZbJmq902nLHfAWN9Y5HElJhHKEvCPTePkKIDQCoUW5RlOFQXKmOtPlUai3BTdArJbv0vPams0wUatkMJTmhlc1FeV6JBZO0Et53e4vy-0tQ5dVXp4RRRUUNr8StuI8_6vj8wUCl72n_bsC-CVh92ADKBakry1rfIUnDAqJonxC38tYHPgj_9mlc_XYQFCEkaj_6XsqMU9Huj_JJmUzAF-KsC7qxfUhd6E2lP0yMZFvxi246bKyWsh_aH8D5sfFAT29_VvHTkEtxKT0ET9YOwFUjxC_s-puCh6UvkcYMiy096dGCDpzuE1LJXo4vGzzcjHDnotO_N1orfsKeHZdIJLYH_GNR6kUmf_y3YjjzmTnx-REc0A8qSnf7Yu7Prpu9HGXnfUFqvWZlrp9tzT-grc8nqr81TmkeD_bpebH1r96hS-tT8BZi0oBM=&#34; alt=&#34;context-diagram-erp&#34;/&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sect2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;_persistence&#34;&gt;Persistence&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sect3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;_folder_structure&#34;&gt;Folder Structure&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Files are written in italics font, folders are written in bold font.&#xA;Examples with content are provided for each file type as test resources.&#xA;These resources are available in the git repository.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;imageblock kroki&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://kroki.io/plantuml/svg/eNqdlcFu4yAQhu99ijm7sp32tL31sveq6gsQM3aIMCDAaaN2330HbCfGSVwrVmIhhp9v5h-QX51n1netfAB6HJM-Dr7jO44-TsNHyLLKtll2nnmEsmSVF14chEdXeHcoyyH4A55twaFhlnnkYNFYdKg880Ir0DUwKSGoSSvQQa0t-B1C